{"tid":558013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情一定有一方付出多啲？","createTime":"2018-02-12T01:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T02:01:22.000Z","uid":38058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"282eed1373e62d47a69e73fccb022923fc870f1f","tid":558013,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"Ex係我追咗兩年先到手，過程中我真係乜都儘量就佢<br />\n因為真係好愛好愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後講分手都係我，因為一直咁用力愛一個人我都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但到依家有其他人倒追我，對我百般遷就，我又覺得我冇可能咁對返佢所以猶疑不決，怕自己做咗當初ex個角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟愛情係咪永遠有一方付出多啲，我應該慶幸自己變成被愛嘅一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c17f869da5f0e716376b5512b6dc720d0bae10d","tid":558013,"uid":140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"GAY POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83163598875c16db9c25a8020d9a471ade92bce","tid":558013,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"要咁計已經唔係愛"},{"pid":"c9f96a64b91af9a9779409853f7e74f89ad47d49","tid":558013,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c17f869da5f0e716376b5512b6dc720d0bae10d","tid":558013,"uid":140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"GAY POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:57:39.000Z","msg":"從何見得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccd4ad417d3bf945e314f45ac8b40a2667480a1","tid":558013,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83163598875c16db9c25a8020d9a471ade92bce","tid":558013,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"要咁計已經唔係愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:01: